      &lt;img alt="coffee machine with hot coffee cup, iced drink with hand pouring cream in, and sugar and coffee pods on a tray." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/38W29_uJwJvm-crQXdepSngHvR0=/3x0:2259x1504/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73504512/Keurig_K_Brew_Chill_Lifestyle_090.0.jpg" /&gt;
