    <title>Gemini intelligence is coming to Google Home </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A pink room with a figure near a Nest Thermostat on the wall and a smart speaker on a table." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/08HowaUr9nGy7iiTyS8LJpp9vNs=/130x0:1071x627/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73504381/Google_Home.0.jpg" /&gt;
